@mcp = http://localhost:5056
# indítás után írd át a portra amit kiír

### list books (via mcp)
GET {{mcp}}/api/mcp/books

### search (via mcp)
GET {{mcp}}/api/mcp/books?q=asimov

### create (via mcp -> book-service)
POST {{mcp}}/api/mcp/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Dune",
  "author": "Frank Herbert",
  "year": 1965
}